# VHS tape for sracha help overview
Output docs/images/help.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontFamily "FiraCode Nerd Font"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 700
Set LetterSpacing 0
Set LineHeight 1.2
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Margin 20
Set BorderRadius 10

Type "sracha --help"
Enter
Sleep 5s
